</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_462" id="230r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_462_r2l19">Karln von <expan>Schawmb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> dem <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_462_r2l20"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> karl als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe Jr in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſchrıft nıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_462_r2l21"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> verſteet denn daʒ wır eẅch dıe ſache <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> Jr vns vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_462_r2l22"><expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> habt meynen ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıehen</expan> / etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol ver - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_462_r2l23"><expan>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅch in dem <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> nehſten brıef </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_462_r2l24"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan> auch noch daʒ wır eẅch von der <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> geſchıcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_462_r2l25"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nıht ſchuldıg ſeyn . wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> / ob Jr vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> on ſprüch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_462_r2l26">nıht laſſen wöltet ſo <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅch dabey <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_462_r2l27">eẅch <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſein <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> / an den <expan>ſtette<ex>n</ex></expan> da wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_462_r2l28">das pıllıchen tun . Das <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> vor <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_463" id="230v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l1"><expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> etc kunıg . / Nu <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l2">Römıſch kunıg . <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> <expan>ynn<ex>er</ex></expan> lands nıht iſt ſo tun wır eẅch ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l3"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır alſo gefreyet vnd <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn . daʒ wır rechtes </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l4"><expan>ſulle<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn . vor der dreyer ſtett Reͣte einem . nemlıch <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l5">winſheım vnd <expan>weıſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / Mugt Jr vns nu vmb dıe <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l6">on ſprüch nıht <expan>gelaſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . ſo <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅch <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſey </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l7"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſeın vor <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> dreyr ſtett Reͣt einem / daʒ Jr <expan>merke<ex>n</ex></expan> mugt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l8">daʒ wır eẅch dıe ſache nıht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıehen</expan> <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd dunkt vns auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l9">daʒ wır eẅch da mıt glimpf vnd rechts gnug pieten / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l10"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Corp<ex>or</ex>ıs</expan> xpı </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_462" id="230r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Karln von <expan>Schawmb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> dem
                            <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Karl, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> schrift niht
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> versteet, denn daz wir ewch die sache,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ir uns vor
                            <expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, meynen zu
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cziehen</expan> etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernome<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Nu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewch in dem
                            <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> nehsten brief
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        auch noch, daz wir ewch von der <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> geschicht
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> niht schuldig seyn; wie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ob ir uns
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> on sprüch niht lassen wöltet, so
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewch dabey
                                <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir ewch
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> sein <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> an den
                                <expan>stette<ex>n</ex></expan>, da wir das pillichen tun, das
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> vor <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <pb facs="#facs_463" id="230v"/>
<expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. kunig. Nu
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der römisch kunig
                            <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan>
<expan>ynn<ex>er</ex></expan> lands niht ist, so tun wir ewch zu
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir also gefreyet und
                                <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn, daz wir rechtes
                                <expan>sulle<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn vor der dreyer stett reͣte
                        einem, nemlich <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, Winsheim und
                                <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>. Mugt ir uns nu umb die
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> sache on sprüch niht
                                <expan>gelass<ex>en</ex></expan>, so <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir ewch <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> sein vor <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        dreyr stett reͣt einem, daz ir <expan>merke<ex>n</ex></expan> mugt, daz wir
                        ewch die sache niht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cziehen</expan>
<expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>; und dunkt uns auch, daz wir ewch damit
                        glimpf und rechts gnug pieten. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> Christi.</ab>
</div>
